UNIVERSAL-Acme version 0.01
===========================

SYNOPSIS

  use UNIVERSAL::Acme;
  UNIVERSAL::thing($obj, 'whatever');  # calls $obj->thing('whatever')

DESCRIPTION

Tired of people who refuse to call functions as methods? Show 'em good with
UNIVERSAL::Acme.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

